    <item>
      <title>引领债务改革的中国开发商再次面临风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/china-developer-that-led-the-way-on-debt-overhaul-at-risk-again</link>
      <description><![CDATA[就在一年多前，融创中国控股有限公司达成了中国房地产行业首笔重大境外债务重组交易，成为中国违约开发商的典范。如今，该公司的问题再次加剧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/china-developer-that-led-the-way-on-debt-overhaul-at-risk-again</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 13 Jan 2025 03:55:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>石油制裁给市场带来冲击，熊市预测受到挑战</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/oil-sanctions-send-a-jolt-through-market-as-bear-case-challenged</link>
      <description><![CDATA[几个月来，全球石油市场的共识是，2025 年将是石油过剩严重、价格持平或疲软的一年。突然间——在美国对俄罗斯能源行业实施迄今为止最大胆的制裁措施之后——前景变得更加复杂。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/oil-sanctions-send-a-jolt-through-market-as-bear-case-challenged</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 13 Jan 2025 03:48:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国人民银行行长潘功胜表示中国将实施更加积极的宏观经济政策</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-01-13/pboc-s-pan-china-will-implement-more-proactive-policies-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国人民银行行长潘功胜在亚洲金融论坛上表示，中国将利用利率等工具维持市场流动性充足。潘功胜周一在香港活动上发表讲话时还表示，人民币“表现出强劲的韧性”。彭博电视台记者刘敏敏报道。（来源：彭博）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-01-13/pboc-s-pan-china-will-implement-more-proactive-policies-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 13 Jan 2025 03:47:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>莱恩称，在风险中欧洲央行可能进一步放松政策</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/more-ecb-policy-policy-easing-in-cards-amid-risks-lane-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲央行首席经济学家菲利普·莱恩表示，欧洲央行可能会进一步降低利率，以确保履行其价格稳定使命。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/more-ecb-policy-policy-easing-in-cards-amid-risks-lane-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 13 Jan 2025 03:43:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>违约建筑商世茂收到新的清盘呈请</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/defaulted-builder-shimao-receives-new-winding-up-petition</link>
      <description><![CDATA[世茂集团控股有限公司在其上一次清盘案被驳回一个月后，在香港再次收到清算申请，这给这家违约建筑商的重组增添了新的不确定性。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/defaulted-builder-shimao-receives-new-winding-up-petition</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 13 Jan 2025 03:31:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国在警告和调整资本管制的同时加大对人民币的支持</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/china-boosts-yuan-support-with-verbal-warning-capital-tweaks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在人民币兑美元在离岸交易中跌至接近历史最低水平后，中国加大了对人民币的支持，誓言打击市场混乱，并调整资本管制。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/china-boosts-yuan-support-with-verbal-warning-capital-tweaks</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 13 Jan 2025 01:22:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国对俄罗斯实施全面制裁后油价创四个月新高</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-12/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-jan-13</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于美国对俄罗斯能源行业实施新一轮制裁，导致本已紧缩的全球市场供应面临压力，油价延续涨势，触及四个多月来最高水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-12/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-jan-13</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 12 Jan 2025 23:02:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>市场综述：亚洲股市下跌，油价因俄罗斯制裁上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-12/asian-stocks-under-pressure-after-blowout-us-jobs-markets-wrap</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周五，美国公布的就业数据强于预期，导致亚洲股市和债市下跌，而因美国对俄罗斯实施新一轮制裁有可能影响石油供应，油价则攀升至四个月高位。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-12/asian-stocks-under-pressure-after-blowout-us-jobs-markets-wrap</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 12 Jan 2025 22:26:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英镑交易员已准备好在抛售后再次下跌 8%</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-12/pound-traders-are-ready-for-another-8-slump-after-market-rout</link>
      <description><![CDATA[期权市场的交易员们正在为英镑进一步下跌 8% 做准备，因为财政问题引发了上周英国股市的惨痛抛售，给英镑造成了压力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-12/pound-traders-are-ready-for-another-8-slump-after-market-rout</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 12 Jan 2025 18:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
